snippet.title: genipool
snippet.description:
Welcome to genipool youtube channel from pool fan and player Evgeny Buslaev aka "genipool".
Main focus here: useful pool drills, licensed clips from "Accu-Stats" tournaments, useful pool drills and also some few other pool videos.
If you like content, subscribe. And fell free to ask whatever you want.

𝐁𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐢𝐧𝐪𝐮𝐢𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐨𝐫 𝐜𝐨𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐫𝐞𝐪𝐮𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐬: 𝐠𝐞𝐧𝐢𝐩𝐨𝐨𝐥𝟏𝟒@𝐠𝐦𝐚𝐢𝐥.𝐜𝐨𝐦 💪
Join Telegram Channel: https://t.me/genipool14
https://www.facebook.com/genipool14
https://www.instagram.com/genipool14/
